Traditional scones are usually sweetened and best enjoyed as a light and delicious treat served with your favourite warm beverages, breakfast juices, and add-ons such as butter, a variety of yummy spreads, cheese, and fruits. These spinach and feta scones, however, are savoury scones and would be better suited with some cold cuts of ham, sweet chilli sauce, strawberry salad, or a fresh side salad.  This recipe was found on sugardishme.com